query:
SELECT 
  SUM(impressions) as totalImpressions,
  SUM(clicks) as totalClicks,
  SUM(spend) as totalSpend,
  SUM(sales) as totalSales,
  SUM(orders) as totalOrders
FROM daily_performance
WHERE accountId = 1 
  AND date >= DATE_SUB(CURDATE(), INTERVAL 30 DAY)
  AND date <= CURDATE();
